Identified Key Classes
1. User

Description:
Represents a generic system user. This is a base class for different user roles.

Key Attributes:

userId

username

password

role

Key Responsibilities:

Authenticate user

Manage user roles

2. Administrator

Description:
Represents the blood bank administrator who manages the system.

Inheritance:

Inherits from User

Key Responsibilities:

Manage donors

Approve or reject blood requests

Generate reports

3. HospitalStaff

Description:
Represents hospital personnel who request blood.

Inheritance:

Inherits from User

Key Responsibilities:

Search blood availability

Request blood

4. AuthorizedStaff

Description:
Represents staff responsible for daily inventory operations.

Inheritance:

Inherits from User

Key Responsibilities:

Update donor details

Manage blood inventory

5. Donor

Description:
Represents a blood donor registered in the system.

Key Attributes:

donorId

name

bloodGroup

contactDetails

lastDonationDate

eligibilityStatus

Key Responsibilities:

Provide donation details

View donation history

6. BloodInventory

Description:
Represents blood stock details maintained by the blood bank.

Key Attributes:

inventoryId

bloodGroup

quantity

expiryDate

Key Responsibilities:

Track available blood units

Monitor expiration

7. BloodRequest

Description:
Represents a request for blood made by hospitals.

Key Attributes:

requestId

bloodGroup

quantity

requestType (Emergency/Normal)

status

Key Responsibilities:

Submit blood request

Track request status

8. Notification

Description:
Represents alerts and messages sent by the system.

Key Attributes:

notificationId

message

date

recipient

Key Responsibilities:

Send alerts to users

Notify donors and staff

9. Report

Description:
Represents system-generated reports.

Key Attributes:

reportId

reportType

generatedDate

Key Responsibilities:

Generate donor and inventory reports


| Class Name      | Type          |
| --------------- | ------------- |
| User            | Base Class    |
| Administrator   | Derived Class |
| HospitalStaff   | Derived Class |
| AuthorizedStaff | Derived Class |
| Donor           | Entity Class  |
| BloodInventory  | Entity Class  |
| BloodRequest    | Entity Class  |
| Notification    | Control Class |
| Report          | Control Class |
